Here is a Cyber SEQ animation file compiled by me.  I don't know who
originally rendered these 40 frames, but they were definately done on
an Atari ST.  The files were ripped off of Compuserve and uploaded to
an ftp site.  I used Cyber Paint to create the SEQ file.

This animation is of the "Lovely Angel" spacecraft from the Japanese
Animation, "Dirty Pair".


